        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>（45g，炮） 生<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="575">狼牙</a>（15g，炙香） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="241">巴豆</a>（15g，去皮心，熬研如脂）<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="123">干姜</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="256">吴茱萸</a>（各15g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上六味，末之，炼蜜丸如桐子大，酒下，强人初服三丸，日三服，弱者二丸。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>治九种心痛。兼治卒中恶，腹胀痛，口不能言。又治连年积冷，流注心胸痛，并冷冲上气，落马坠车血疾等，皆主之。忌口如常法。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'二陈汤（太平惠民和剂局方）','null','<section>
