        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="123">干姜</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="40">白术</a>（各9g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上四味，以水八升，煮取三升，温服一升，日三服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>理中加桂人参汤，阳复阴邪自散藏，休讶补攻分两道，道消道长细推详。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>胸痹，心中<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1348">痞</a>气，气结在胸，胸满，胁下逆抢心，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="318">枳实薤白桂枝汤</a>主之，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="319">人参汤</a>亦主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
