    <p>《医方考》卷二
《医方考》卷三
《医方考》卷四





</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="52">熟地黄</a>（八两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="18">山药</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="234">山茱萸</a>（各四两，净肉） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="162">牡丹皮</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="129">泽泻</a> 白<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="348">茯苓</a>（各三两）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>阴虚于下，令人多呕者，主此方<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="53255">盐汤</a>吞之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《时方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>六味滋阴益肾肝，茱薯丹泽地苓丸，再加桂附挟真火，八味功同九转丹。</dd></p><p><dt>《方剂学》邓中甲</dt></p><p><dd>六味地黄山药萸，泽泻苓丹“三泻”侣，三阴并补重滋肾，肾阴不足效可居，滋阴降火知柏需，养肝明目加杞菊，都气五味纳肾气，滋补肺肾麦味续。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>肾虚移热于肺，咳嗽者。</dd></p><p><dd>肾虚不能制火者。</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2142">下消</a>者，烦渴引饮，小便如膏。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'六味地黄丸（鲁府禁方）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《鲁府禁方》卷二&middot;寿集

</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>大怀<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="50">生地黄</a>（用好酒拌炒，锅<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1954">内蒸</a>熟取出，再用<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="283">砂仁</a>一两、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="348">茯苓</a>二两，二味用绢袋包，藏在<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="50">地黄</a>内，用酒浸平，慢火煮干，去砂、茯不用，竹刀切碎，晒干，八两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="234">山茱萸</a>（酒蒸去核，四两） 白<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="348">茯苓</a>（去皮，三两） 干<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="18">山药</a>（四两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="162">牡丹皮</a>（去<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="25320">骨</a>，三两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="129">泽泻</a>（二两）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上忌<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="559">铁</a>器，为细末，用前<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="67828">参术膏</a>为丸，如梧子大。每服三钱，空心米汤下，（此方只用半料，后又制入<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="493">鹿角胶</a>四两为丸，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="670">乳汁</a>下。又日进<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="670">乳汁</a>三四次效）。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>养心滋肾，补肺健脾，清热除湿。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
