        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>赤斑咽痛毒为阳，鳖甲周围一指量，半两雄黄升二两，椒归一两草同行。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>阳毒之为病，面赤斑斑如锦文，咽喉痛，唾脓血。五日可治，七日不可治，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="288">升麻鳖甲汤</a>主之。</dd></p><p><dd>阴毒之为病，面目青，身痛如被杖，咽喉痛。五日可治，七日不可治，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="288">升麻鳖甲汤</a>去<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="223">雄黄</a><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="263">蜀椒</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>随证化裁</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>阴毒之为病，面目青，身痛如被杖，咽喉痛。五日可治，七日不可治，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="288">升麻鳖甲汤</a>去<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="223">雄黄</a>、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="263">蜀椒</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'半夏厚朴汤（金匮要略）','null','<section>
