    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>（洗） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>（去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（炙）</dd>
