    <dl>
<dd>右七味，以水一斗，煮取六升，去滓，再煎，取三升，温服一升，日三服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>三两姜参炙草芩，一连痞证呕多寻，半升半夏枣十二，去滓重煎守古箴。</dd></p><p><dt>《方剂学》邓中甲</dt></p><p><dd>半夏泻心配芩连，干姜人参草枣全，辛开苦降除痞满，寒热错杂痞证蠲。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法下</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="688">第149条</a>  伤寒五六日，呕而发热者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="750">柴胡汤</a>证具，而以他药下之，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="95">柴胡</a>证仍在者，复与<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="750">柴胡汤</a>，此虽已下之，不为逆，必蒸蒸而振，却发热汗出而解；若心下满而硬痛者，此为<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1885">结胸</a>也，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="174">大陷胸汤</a>主之；但满而不痛者，此为<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1348">痞</a>，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="95">柴胡</a>不中与也，宜<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="180">半夏泻心汤</a>。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
