        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法中</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="605">第66条</a>  发汗后，腹胀满者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="164">厚朴</a><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="6385">半夏人参汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
