<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="316">莲子</a>肉（去皮）、 <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="331">薏苡仁</a>、 <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="283">缩砂仁</a>、 <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="97">桔梗</a>（炒令深黄色），各480g， <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="253">白扁豆</a>（姜汁浸，去皮，微炒），720g，白<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="348">茯苓</a>，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>（去芦）、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>(炒）、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="40">白术</a>、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="18">山药</a>，各960g。</dd>
    </dl>
