    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上各<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1488">㕮</a>咀，分为三贴，一贴以水三升，煮取二升，分温三服；如人行四<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="acupoint" object-id="111">五里</a>进一服。如四体壅，添<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>少许，每贴分作三小贴，每小贴以水一升，煮取七合，温服，再合滓为一服。重煮都成四服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>退五脏虚热。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'四物汤（太平惠民和剂局方）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《太平惠民和剂局方》卷九






</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="16033">当归</a>（去芦，酒浸，炒） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="21">川芎</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">白芍药</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="52">熟干地黄</a>（酒洒，蒸，各等分）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="16033">当归</a>（去芦，酒浸，炒） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="21">川芎</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">白芍药</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="52">熟干地黄</a>（酒洒，蒸，各等分）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上为粗末。每服三钱，水一盏半，煎至八分，去渣，热服空心，食前。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>调益荣卫，滋养气血。治冲任虚损，月水不调，脐腹<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2159">㽲</a>痛，崩中漏下，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1991">血瘕</a>块硬，发歇疼痛，妊娠宿冷，将理失宜，胎动不安，血下不止，及产后乘虚风寒内搏，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2036">恶露</a>不下，结生<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1400">瘕</a>聚，少腹坚痛，时作寒热。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>随证化裁</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>若妊娠胎动不安，下血不止者，加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="176">艾</a>十叶，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="366">阿胶</a>一片，同煎如前法。或血脏虚冷，崩中去血过多，亦加胶、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="176">艾</a>煎。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'四逆加人参汤（伤寒论）','null','<section>
