    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>右三味，以水三升，煮取一升二合，去滓，分温再服，强人可大<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>一枚，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="123">干姜</a>三两。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>生附一枚两半姜，草须二两少阴方，建功姜附如良将，将将从容藉草匡。</dd></p><p><dt>《汤头歌诀》汪昂</dt></p><p><dd>四逆汤中姜附草，三阴厥逆太阳沉。或盖姜葱参芍桔，通阳复脉力能任。</dd></p><p><dt>《方剂学》邓中甲</dt></p><p><dd>四逆汤中附草姜，阳衰寒厥急煎尝，腹痛吐泻脉沉细，急投此方可回阳。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法上</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="568">第29条</a>   伤寒脉浮，自汗出，小便数，心烦，微恶寒，脚挛急，反与<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="93">桂枝汤</a>，欲攻其表，此误也，得之便厥。咽中干，烦燥，吐逆者，作<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="102">甘草干姜汤</a>与之，以复其阳。若厥愈、足温者，更作<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="103">芍药甘草汤</a>与之，其脚即伸。若胃气不和，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1825">谵语</a>者，少与<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="54644">调胃承气汤</a>。若重发汗，复加烧针者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="10">四逆汤</a>主之。</dd></p><p><dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法中</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="630">第91条</a>  伤寒，医下之，续得下利，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1846">清谷</a>不止，身疼痛者，急当救里；后身疼痛，清便自调者，急当救表。救里宜<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="10">四逆汤</a>；救表宜<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="93">桂枝汤</a>。</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="631">第92条</a>  病发热头痛，脉反沉，若不差，身体疼痛，当救其里，宜<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="10">四逆汤</a>。</dd></p><p><dd>辨阳明病脉证并治法</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="764">第225条</a>  脉浮而迟，表热里寒，下利<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1846">清谷</a>者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="10">四逆汤</a>主之。</dd></p><p><dd>辨太阴病脉证并治法</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="816">第277条</a>  自利不渴者，属太阴，以其脏有寒故也，当温之，宜服<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1978">四逆</a>辈。</dd></p><p><dd>辨少阴病脉证并治法</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="862">第323条</a>  少阴病，脉沉者，急温之，宜<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="10">四逆汤</a>。</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="863">第324条</a>  少阴病，饮食入口则吐，心中温温，欲吐复不能吐。始得之，手足寒，脉弦迟者，此胸中饮实，不可下也，当吐之；若<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1195">膈</a>上有寒饮，干呕者，不可吐也，宜<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="10">四逆汤</a>。</dd></p><p><dd>辨厥阴病脉证并治法</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="892">第353条</a>  大汗出，热不去，内拘急，四肢疼，又下利，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1607">厥逆</a>而恶寒者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="10">四逆汤</a>主之。</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="893">第354条</a>  大汗，若大下利而厥冷者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="10">四逆汤</a>主之。</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="911">第372条</a>  下利，腹胀满，身体疼痛者，先温其里，乃攻其表，温里宜<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="10">四逆汤</a>，攻表宜<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="93">桂枝汤</a>。</dd></p><p><dd>辨霍乱病脉证并治法</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="927">第388条</a>  吐利汗出，发热恶寒，四肢拘急，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2122">手足厥冷</a>者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="10">四逆汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'四逆汤（金匮要略）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《金匮要略》卷中呕吐哕下利病脉证治第十七





</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>（一枚，生用） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="123">干姜</a>（一两半） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（二两，炙）‍</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>（6g，生用） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="123">干姜</a>（4.5g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（6g，炙）‍</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上三味，以水三升，煮取一升二合，去滓，分温再服。强人可大<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>一枚，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="123">干姜</a>三两。‍</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>生附一枚两半姜，草须二两少阴方，建功姜附如良将，将将从容藉草匡。</dd></p><p><dt>《汤头歌诀》汪昂</dt></p><p><dd>四逆汤中姜附草，三阴厥逆太阳沉。或盖姜葱参芍桔，通阳复脉力能任。</dd></p><p><dt>《方剂学》邓中甲</dt></p><p><dd>四逆汤中附草姜，阳衰寒厥急煎尝，腹痛吐泻脉沉细，急投此方可回阳。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>呕而脉弱，小便复利，身有微热，见厥者，难治，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="10">四逆汤</a>主之。</dd></p><p><dd>下利，腹胀满，身体疼痛者，先温其里，乃攻其表。温里宜<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="10">四逆汤</a>，攻表直<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="93">桂枝汤</a>。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'土瓜根散（金匮要略）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《金匮要略》卷下妇人杂病脉证并治第二十二






</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="526">土瓜根</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>  <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="357">蟅虫</a>（各三分）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="526">土瓜根</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="357">蟅虫</a>（各11.3g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上四味，杵为散，酒服<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2172">方寸匕</a>，日三服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>带下端由瘀血停，月间再见不循经，蟅瓜桂芍均相等，调协阴阳病自宁。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>带下经水不利，少腹满痛，经一月再见者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="492">土瓜根散</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'大乌头煎（金匮要略）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《金匮要略》卷上腹满寒疝宿食病脉证治第十





</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="67">乌头</a>（大者五枚，熬，去皮，不<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1488">㕮</a>咀）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="67">乌头</a>（5g，熬，去皮，不<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1488">㕮</a>咀）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上以水三升，煮取一升，去滓，内蜜二升，煎令水气尽，取二升，强人服七合，弱人服五合。不差，明日更服，不可一日再服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>沉紧而弦痛绕脐，白津厥逆冷凄凄，乌头五个煮添蜜，顷刻颠危快挈提。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>腹痛，脉弦而紧，弦则卫气不行，即恶寒；紧则不欲食，邪正相搏，即为<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2299">寒疝</a>。<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2299">寒疝</a>绕脐痛，若发则<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2283">白汗</a>出，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2122">手足厥冷</a>，其脉沉弦者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="362">大乌头煎</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'大半夏汤（金匮要略）','null','<section>
