    <p>《金匮要略》卷中呕吐哕下利病脉证治第十七




</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>（二升，洗完用） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>（三两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="496">白蜜</a>（一升）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>（30g，洗完用） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>（9g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="496">白蜜</a>（40ml）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上三味，以水一斗二升，和蜜扬之二百四十遍，煮药取二升半，温服一升，余分再服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>从来胃反责冲乘，半夏二升蜜一升，三两人参劳水煮，纳冲养液有奇能。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>胃反呕吐者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="455">大半夏汤</a>主之。（《千金》云：治胃反，不受食，食入即吐。《外台》云：治呕，心下<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1348">痞</a>硬者）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'大建中汤（金匮要略）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《金匮要略》卷上腹满寒疝宿食病脉证治第十








