    <p>《伤寒论》













</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="14483">大黄</a>（四两，酒洗） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="164">厚朴</a>（半斤，炙，去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="277">枳实</a>（五枚，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="217">芒硝</a>（三合）</dd>
