</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="14483">大黄</a>（三两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>（三枚，炮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="105">细辛</a>（二两）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="14483">大黄</a>（9g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>（12g，炮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="105">细辛</a>（6g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上三味，以水五升，煮取二升，分温三服。若强人煮取二升半，分温三服，服后如人行四<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="acupoint" object-id="111">五里</a>，进一服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《汤头歌诀》汪昂</dt></p><p><dd>附子泻心用三黄，寒加热药以维阳。痞乃热邪寒药治，恶寒加附治相当。大黄附子汤同意，温药下之妙异常。</dd></p><p><dt>《方剂学》邓中甲</dt></p><p><dd>金匮大黄附子汤，细辛散寒止痛良， 温下治法代表方，寒积里实服之康。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>胁下偏痛，发热，其脉紧弦，此寒也，以温药下之。宜<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="360">大黄附子汤</a>。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'大黄黄连泻心汤（伤寒论）','null','<section>
