        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>师曰：病有<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2091">奔豚</a>，有吐脓，有惊怖，有火邪，此四部病，皆从惊发得之。师曰：<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2091">奔豚</a>病从少腹起，上冲咽喉，发作欲死，复还止，皆从惊恐得之。</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2091">奔豚</a>，气上冲胸，腹痛，往来寒热，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="315">奔豚汤</a>主之。</dd>
