    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>呕家见渴饮当除，不渴应知支饮居，半夏一升姜八两，源头探得病根锄。</dd></p><p><dt>《方剂学》邓中甲</dt></p><p><dd>小半夏汤有生姜，化痰降逆基础方， 主治痰饮呕吐证，若加茯苓效力彰。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>呕家本渴，渴者为欲解，今反不渴，心下有<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1681">支饮</a>故也，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="371">小半夏汤</a>主之（卷中<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1683">痰饮</a>咳嗽病脉证并治第十二）</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2231">黄疸</a>病，小便色不变，欲自利，腹满而喘，不可除热，热除必<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1525">哕</a>；<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1525">哕</a>者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="371">小半夏汤</a>主之。（<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2231">黄疸</a>病脉证并治第十五）</dd></p><p><dd>诸呕吐，谷不得下者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="371">小半夏汤</a>主之。（呕吐<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1525">哕</a>下利病脉证治第十七）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'小建中汤（伤寒论）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《伤寒论》辨太阳病脉证并治法中第六












</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>（三两，去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（二两，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（十二枚，擘） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a>（六两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（三两，切） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="634">胶饴</a>（一升）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>（9g，去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（6g，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（3枚，擘） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a>（18g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（9g，切） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="634">胶饴</a>（30g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>右六味，以水七升，煮取三升，去滓，内<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="634">胶饴</a>，更上微火消解，温服一升，日三服。呕家不可用<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="37412">建中汤</a>，以甜故也。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>建中即是桂枝汤，倍芍加饴绝妙方，饴取一升六两芍，悸烦腹痛有奇长。</dd></p><p><dt>《汤头歌诀》汪昂</dt></p><p><dd>小建中汤芍药多，桂姜甘草大枣和。更加饴糖补中脏，虚劳腹冷服之瘥。增入黄芪名亦尔，表虚身痛效无过。又有建中十四味，阴班劳损起沉疴。十全大补加附子，麦夏苁蓉仔细哦。</dd></p><p><dt>《方剂学》邓中甲</dt></p><p><dd>小建中汤君饴糖，方含桂枝加芍汤，温中补虚和缓急，虚劳里急腹痛康。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法中</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="639">第100条</a>  伤寒，阳脉涩，阴脉弦，法当腹中急痛者，先与<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="155">小建中汤</a>；不差者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="153">小柴胡汤</a>主之。</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="641">第102条</a>  伤寒二三日，心中<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2092">悸</a>而烦者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="155">小建中汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
