<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="417">麻黄</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="105">细辛</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="123">干姜</a>（各三两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="237">五味子</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>（各半升） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="214">石膏</a>（二两）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
