        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="417">麻黄</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="105">细辛</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="123">干姜</a>（各9g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="237">五味子</a>（6g）<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>（10g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="214">石膏</a>（6g）</dd>
