    <p>《伤寒论》















</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="417">麻黄</a>（三两，去节） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a>（三两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="123">干姜</a>（三两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（三两，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>（三两，去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="105">细辛</a>（三两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="237">五味子</a>（半升） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>（半升，洗）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="417">麻黄</a>（9g，去节） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a>（9g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="123">干姜</a>（9g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（9g，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>（9g，去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="105">细辛</a>（9g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="237">五味子</a>（6g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>（9g，洗）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>右八味，以水一斗，先煮<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="417">麻黄</a>，减二升，去上沫，内诸药，煮取三升，去滓，温服一升。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>桂麻姜芍草辛三，夏味半升记要谙，表不解兮心下水，咳而发热句中探。</dd></p><p><dt>《汤头歌诀》汪昂</dt></p><p><dd>小龙青汤治水气，喘咳呕哕渴利慰。姜桂麻黄芍药甘，细辛半夏兼五味。</dd></p><p><dt>《方剂学》邓中甲</dt></p><p><dd>解表蠲饮小青龙，麻桂姜辛夏草从，芍药五味敛气阴，表寒内饮最有功。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法中</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="579">第40条</a>  伤寒表不解，心下有水气，干呕发热而咳，或渴，或利，或噎，或小便不利，少腹满，或喘者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="111">小青龙汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>随证化裁</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>若渴，去<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>，加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="10">栝蒌根</a>三两；若微利，去<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="417">麻黄</a>，加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="192">芫花</a>，如一鸡子，熬令赤色；若噎者，去<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="417">麻黄</a>，加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>一枚，炮；若小便不利、少腹满者，去<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="417">麻黄</a>，加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="348">茯苓</a>四两；若喘，去<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="417">麻黄</a>，加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="270">杏仁</a>半升，去皮尖。且<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="192">芫花</a>不治利。<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="417">麻黄</a>主喘，今此语反之，疑非仲景意。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
