</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'当归生姜羊肉汤（金匮要略）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《金匮要略》卷上腹满寒疝宿食病脉证治第十
卷下妇人产后病脉证治第二十一





</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="16033">当归</a>（三两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（五两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="642">羊肉</a>（一斤）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="16033">当归</a>（9g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（15g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="642">羊肉</a>（48g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上三味，以水八升，煮取三升，温服七合，日三服。若寒多者，加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>成一斤；痛多而呕者，加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="299">橘皮</a>二两、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="40">白术</a>一两。加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>者，亦加水五升，煮取三升二合，服之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《汤头歌诀》汪昂</dt></p><p><dd>当归生姜羊肉汤，产后腹痛蓐劳匡。亦有加入参芪者，千金四物甘桂姜。</dd></p><p><dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>腹痛胁痛急不堪，羊斤姜五并归三，于今豆蔻香砂法，可笑依盲授指南。寒多增到一斤姜，痛呕宜加橘术商，术用一兮橘二两，祛痰止呕补中方。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2299">寒疝</a>，腹中痛及胁痛<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1665">里急</a>者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="363">当归生姜羊肉汤</a>主之。（卷上腹满<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2299">寒疝</a>宿食病脉证治第十）</dd></p><p><dd>产后腹中疞痛，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="363">当归生姜羊肉汤</a>主之；并治腹中<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2299">寒疝</a>，虚劳不足。（卷下妇人产后病脉证治第二十一）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
