<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="378">文蛤</a>（75g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上一味为散，以沸汤和一<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2172">方寸匕</a>服，汤用五合。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>水噀原逾汗法门，肉中粟起更增烦。意中思水还无渴，文蛤磨调药不繁。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法下</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="680">第141条</a>  病在阳，应以汗解之，反以冷水<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1560">潠</a>之；若灌之，其热被却不得去，弥更益烦，肉上粟起，意欲饮水，反不渴者，服<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="177">文蛤散</a>；若不差者，与<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="126">五苓散</a>。寒实<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1885">结胸</a>，无热证者，与<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="176">三物白散</a>，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="11">小陷胸汤</a>不可服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'文蛤散（金匮要略）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《金匮要略》卷中消渴小便不利淋病脉证并治第十三



</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="378">文蛤</a>（五两）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="378">文蛤</a>（15g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上一味，杵为散，以沸汤五合，和服<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2172">方寸匕</a>。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>水噀原逾汗法门，肉中粟起更增烦。意中思水还无渴，文蛤磨调药不繁。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>厥阴之为病，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1889">消渴</a>，气上冲心，心中疼热，饥而不欲食，食即吐蛔，下之不肯止。寸口脉浮而迟，浮即为虚，迟即为劳；虚则卫气不足，劳则荣气竭。<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2216">趺阳</a>脉浮而数，浮即为气，数即为<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2041">消谷</a>而大坚（一作紧）。气盛则<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="543">溲</a>数，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="543">溲</a>数即坚，坚数相搏，即为<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1889">消渴</a>。</dd></p><p><dd>渴欲饮水不止者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="177">文蛤散</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
