<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>（去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="108">黄芩</a>（各一两半） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a>（一两半） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>（一两半） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（一两，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>（二合半，洗） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（六枚，擘） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（一两半，切） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="95">柴胡</a>（四两）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>（去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="108">黄芩</a>（各4.5g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a>（4.5g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>（4.5g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（3g，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>（6g，洗） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（1枚，擘） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（4.5g，切） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="95">柴胡</a>（12g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>右九味，以水七升，煮取三升，去滓，温服一升。本云：<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="319">人参汤</a>，作如<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>法，加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="95">柴胡</a>、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="108">黄芩</a>；复如<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="95">柴胡</a>法，今用<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>作半剂。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>小柴原方取半煎，桂枝汤入复方全，阳中太小相因病，偏重柴胡作仔肩。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法下</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="685">第146条</a>  伤寒六七日，发热，微恶寒，支节烦疼，微呕，心下支结，外证未去者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="178">柴胡桂枝汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
