<dd>太阳病，其证备，身体强，几几然，脉反沉迟，此为<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1338">痓</a>（一本作痉）。<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="279">栝蒌桂枝汤</a>主之。</dd>
