<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>（五两，去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a>（三两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（三两，切） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（二两，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（十二枚，擘）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>（15g，去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a>（9g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（9g，切） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（6g，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（3枚，擘）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>右五味，以水七升，煮取三升，去滓，温服一升。本云：<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="93">桂枝汤</a>，今加桂满五两。所以加桂者，以泄<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2091">奔豚</a>气也。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>气从脐逆号奔豚，汗为烧针启病源，只取桂枝汤本味，再加二两桂枝论。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法中</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="656">第117条</a>  烧针令其汗，针处被寒，核起而赤者，必发<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2091">奔豚</a>，气从少腹上冲心者，灸其核上各一壮，与<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="164">桂枝加桂汤</a>。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
