        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（各9g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（6g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（3枚） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="443">龙骨</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="365">牡蛎</a>（各9g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上七味，以水七升，煮取三升，分温三服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>男子失精女梦交，坎离救治在中爻，桂枝汤内加龙牡，三两相匀要细敲。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;男子面色薄者，主渴及亡血，卒喘<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2092">悸</a>，脉浮者里虚也。男子脉虚沉弦，无寒热，短气，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1665">里急</a>，小便不利，面色白，时目瞑兼<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="538">衄</a>，少腹满，此为劳使之然。劳之为病，其脉浮大，手足烦，春夏剧，秋冬瘥，阴寒精自出，酸削不能行。</dd></p><p><dd>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;男子脉浮弱而涩，为无子，精气清冷（一作冷）。夫失精家，少腹弦急，阴头寒，目眩（一作目眶痛）发落，脉极虚<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2217">芤</a>迟，为<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1846">清谷</a>亡血失精；脉得诸<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2217">芤</a>动微紧，男子失精，女子梦交，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="300">桂枝加龙骨牡蛎汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'桂枝去桂加白术汤（伤寒论）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《伤寒论》











</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>（三枚，炮，去皮，破） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="40">白术</a>（四两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（三两，切） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（二两，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（十二枚，擘）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>（6g，炮，去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="40">白术</a>（12g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（9g，切） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（6g，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（2枚，擘）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>右五味，以水六升，煮取二升，去滓，分温三服，初一服，其人身如痹，半日许复服之，三服都尽，其人如冒状，勿怪，此以<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="40">白术</a>并走皮内，逐水气未得除，故使之耳，法当加桂四两，此本一方二法，以大便硬，小便自利，去桂；以大便不硬，小便不利，当加桂，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>三枚恐多也，虚弱家及产妇，宜减服之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>大便如硬小便通，脉涩虚浮湿胜风，即用前方须去桂，术加四两有神功。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法下</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="713">第174条</a>  伤寒，八九日，风湿相搏，身体烦疼，不能自转侧，不呕，不渴，脉浮虚而涩者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="193">桂枝附子汤</a>主之；若其人大便硬（一云脐下心下硬），小便自利者，去<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="68143">白术汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
