    <dl>
<dd>右六味，以水八升，煮取三升，去滓，温服半升，日三服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>冲气低时咳满频，前方去桂益姜辛，姜辛三两依原法，原法通微便出新。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>咳满即止，而更复渴，冲气复发者，以<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="105">细辛</a>、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="123">干姜</a>为热药也。服之当遂渴，而渴反止者，为<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1681">支饮</a>也。<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1681">支饮</a>者，法当冒，冒者必呕，呕者复内<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>，以去其水。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
