        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="348">茯苓</a>（12g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>（12g，去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（9g，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="237">五味子</a>（6g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>右四味，以水八升，煮取三升，去滓，分三温服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>青龙却碍肾元亏，上逆下流又冒时，味用半升苓桂四，甘三扶土镇冲宜。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="61979">青龙汤</a>下已，多唾口燥，寸脉沉，尺脉微，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2123">手足厥逆</a>，气从小腹上冲胸咽，手足痹，其面<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1554">翕</a>热如醉状，因复下流阴股，小便难，时复冒者；与<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="348">茯苓</a><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>五味<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="215">甘草汤</a>，治其<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="acupoint" object-id="361">气冲</a>。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'桃核承气汤（伤寒论）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《伤寒论》












</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="294">桃仁</a>（五十个，去皮尖） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>（二两，去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="14483">大黄</a>（四两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="217">芒硝</a>（二两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（二两，炙）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="294">桃仁</a>（12g，去皮尖） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>（6g，去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="14483">大黄</a>（12g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="217">芒硝</a>（6g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（6g，炙）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>右五味，以水七升，煮取二升半，去滓，内<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="217">芒硝</a>，更上火，微沸下火，先食温服五合，日三服，当微利。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>五十桃仁四两黄，桂硝二两草同行，膀胱热结如狂证，外解方攻用此汤。</dd></p><p><dt>《汤头歌诀》汪昂</dt></p><p><dd>桃仁承气五般奇，甘草硝黄并桂枝。热结膀胱少腹胀，如狂蓄血最相宜。</dd></p><p><dt>《方剂学》邓中甲</dt></p><p><dd>桃核承气硝黄草，少佐桂枝温通妙，下焦蓄血小腹胀，泻热破瘀微利效。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法中</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="645">第106条</a>  太阳病不解，热结膀胱，其人如狂，血自下，下者愈。其外不解者，尚未可攻，当先解外。外解已，但少腹急结者，乃可攻之，宜<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="160">桃核承气汤</a>。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
