<dd>辨少阴病脉证并治法</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="845">第306条</a>  少阴病，下利便脓血者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="213">桃花汤</a>主之。</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="846">第307条</a>  少阴病，二三日至四五日，腹痛，小便不利，下利不止，便脓血者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="213">桃花汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
