            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>病瘥腰下水偏停，泽泻蒌根蜀漆葶，牡蛎商陆同海藻，捣称等分饮调灵。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨阴阳易差后劳复病证并治法</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="934">第395条</a>  大病差后，从腰以下有水气者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="236">牡蛎泽泻散</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'独活寄生汤（太平惠民和剂局方）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《太平惠民和剂局方》卷五
</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="130">独活</a>（三两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="411">桑寄生</a>（古今录验，用<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="136">续断</a>，即寄生亦名，非正<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="136">续断</a>） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="16033">当归</a>（酒浸，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1962">焙</a>干） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">白芍药</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="52">熟地黄</a>（酒浸，蒸） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="28">牛膝</a>（去芦，酒浸） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="105">细辛</a>（去苗） 白<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="348">茯苓</a>（去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="61">防风</a>（去芦） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="100">秦艽</a>（去土） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2200">桂心</a>（不见火） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="21">芎䓖</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="160">杜仲</a>（制炒断丝） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（炙，各二两）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="130">独活</a>（90g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="411">桑寄生</a>（《古今录验》用<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="136">续断</a>，即寄生亦名，非正<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="136">续断</a>）、 <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="16033">当归</a>（酒浸，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1962">焙</a>干）、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">白芍药</a>、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="52">熟地黄</a>（酒浸，蒸）、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="28">牛膝</a>（去芦，酒浸)、 <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="105">细辛</a>（去苗）、白<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="348">茯苓</a>（去皮）、 <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="61">防风</a>（去芦）、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="100">秦艽</a>（去土）、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2200">桂心</a>（不见火）、芎、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="160">杜仲</a>（制，炒断丝）、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（炙），各60g。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上为<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="760">锉散</a>。每服四大钱，水一盏半，煎七分，去滓，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2398">空心服</a>。气虚下痢，除<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="50">地黄</a>。并治新产腹痛，不得转动，及腰脚挛<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1714">痛痹</a>弱，不得屈伸。此汤最能除风消血。（肘后方）有<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>一枚，无寄生。<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>。<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="16033">当归</a>。近人将治<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2306">历节</a>风并脚气流注，甚有效。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>肾气虚弱，腰背疼痛，此病因卧冷湿地当风所得，不时速治，流入脚膝，为偏枯冷痹，缓弱疼重。或腰痛脚重、挛痹，宜急服此。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
