    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'猪苓汤（伤寒论）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《伤寒论》











</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="353">猪苓</a>（去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="348">茯苓</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="129">泽泻</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="366">阿胶</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="30061">滑石</a>（碎）（各一两）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="353">猪苓</a>（去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="348">茯苓</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="129">泽泻</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="366">阿胶</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="30061">滑石</a>（碎）（各3g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>右五味，以水四升，先煮四味，取二升，去滓，内<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="366">阿胶</a>烊消，温服七合，日三服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>泽胶猪茯滑相连，咳呕心烦渴不眠，煮好去滓胶后入，育阴利水法兼全。</dd></p><p><dt>《汤头歌诀》汪昂</dt></p><p><dd>五苓散治太阳腑，白术泽泻猪茯苓。膀胱化气添官桂，利便消暑烦渴清。除桂名为四苓散，无寒但渴服之灵。猪苓汤除桂与术，加入阿胶滑石停。此为利湿兼泻热，疸黄便闭渴呕宁。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨阳明病脉证并治法</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="762">第223条</a>  若脉浮发热，渴欲饮水，小便不利者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="199">猪苓汤</a>主之。</dd></p><p><dd>辨少阴病脉证并治法</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="858">第319条</a>  少阴病，下利六七日，小便不利，咳而呕，渴，心烦不得眠者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="199">猪苓汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
