    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（12g，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="108">黄芩</a>（9g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>（9g，洗） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（3枚，擘） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="31341">黄连</a>（3g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="123">干姜</a>（9g）</dd>
    </dl>
