        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>下余痞作腹雷鸣，甘四姜芩三两平，一两黄连半升夏，枣枚十二擘同烹。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法下</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="697">第158条</a>  伤寒中风，医反下之，其人下利，日数十行，谷不化，腹中雷鸣，心下<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1348">痞</a>鞭而满，干呕，心烦不得安，医见心下<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1348">痞</a>，谓病不尽，复下之，其<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1348">痞</a>益甚，此非热结，但以胃中虚，客气上结，故使鞭也，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="185">甘草泻心汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
