    <p>《金匮要略》卷下妇人妊娠病脉证并治第二十






</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="40">白术</a>（四分） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="21">芎䓖</a>（四分） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="263">蜀椒</a>（三分，去汗） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="365">牡蛎</a>（二分）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="40">白术</a>（15g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="21">芎䓖</a>（15g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="263">蜀椒</a>（11.3g，去汗） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="365">牡蛎</a>（7.5g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上四味，杵为散，酒服一<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2173">钱匕</a>，日三服，夜一服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>胎由土载术之功，养血相资妙有芎，阴气上凌椒摄下，牡潜龙性得真诠。苦痛芍药加最美，心下毒痛倚芎是，吐痛不食心又烦，加夏廿枚一细使，醋浆水须服后吞，若还不呕药可止，不解小麦煮汁尝，已后渴者大麦喜；既愈常服勿轻抛，壶中阴阳大燮理。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>妊娠养胎，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="483">白术散</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>随证化裁</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>但苦痛加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a>；心下毒痛倍加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="21">芎䓖</a>；心烦吐痛不能食饮，加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="105">细辛</a>一两、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>大者二十枚。服之后，更以<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="518">醋浆</a>水服之；若呕，以<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="518">醋浆</a>水服之，复不解者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="632">小麦</a>汁服之；已后渴者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="15105">大麦粥</a>服之。病虽愈，服之勿置。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'白术附子汤（金匮要略）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《金匮要略》卷上痓湿暍病脉证第二






</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="40">白术</a>（二两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>（一枚半，炮去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（一两，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（一两半，切）<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（六枚）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="40">白术</a>（6g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>（6g，炮去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（3g，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（4.5g，切）<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（2枚）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上五味，以水三升，煮取一升，去滓，分温三服。一服觉身痹，半日许再服，三服都尽，其人如冒状，勿怪，即是术附并走皮中，逐水气未得除故耳。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>大便若硬小便通，脉涩虚浮湿胜风，即用前方去桂枝，术加四两有神功。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>伤寒八九日，风湿相搏，身体疼烦，不能自转侧，不呕不渴，脉浮虚而涩者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="193">桂枝附子汤</a>主之；若大便坚，小便自利者，去桂加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="68143">白术汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'白虎加人参汤（伤寒论）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《伤寒论》











</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="76">知母</a>（六两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="214">石膏</a>（一斤，碎，绵裹） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（三两，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="462">粳米</a>（六合） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>（三两）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="76">知母</a>（18g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="214">石膏</a>（48g，碎，绵裹） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（9g，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="462">粳米</a>（30g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>（9g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>右五味，以水一斗，煮米熟汤成，去滓，温服一升，日三服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>服桂渴烦大汗倾，液亡肌腠涸阳明，膏斤知六参三两，二草六粳米熟成。</dd></p><p><dt>《汤头歌诀》汪昂</dt></p><p><dd>白虎汤用石膏偎，知母甘草粳米陪。亦有加入人参者，躁烦热渴舌生苔。</dd></p><p><dt>《方剂学》邓中甲</dt></p><p><dd>白虎膏知粳米甘，清热生津止渴烦，气分热盛四大证，益气生津人参添。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法上</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="565">第26条</a>  服<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="93">桂枝汤</a>，大汗出后，大烦渴不解，脉洪大者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="99">白虎加人参汤</a>主之。</dd></p><p><dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法下</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="707">第168条</a>  伤寒，若吐，若下后，七八日不解，热结在里，表里俱热，时时恶风，大渴，舌上干燥而烦，欲饮水数升者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="99">白虎加人参汤</a>主之。</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="708">第169条</a>  伤寒，无大热，口燥渴，心烦，背微恶寒者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="99">白虎加人参汤</a>主之。</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="709">第170条</a>  伤寒，脉浮，发热，无汗，其表不解者，不可与<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="4368">白虎汤</a>，渴欲饮水，无表证者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="99">白虎加人参汤</a>主之。</dd></p><p><dd>辨阳明病脉证并治法</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="761">第222条</a>  若渴欲饮水，口干舌燥者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="99">白虎加人参汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
