        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="76">知母</a>（18g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="214">石膏</a>（48g，碎） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（6g，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="462">粳米</a>（21克）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上四味，以水一斗，煮米熟，汤成去滓，温服一升，日三服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>阳明白虎辨非难，难在阳邪背恶寒，知六膏斤甘二两，米加六合服之安。</dd></p><p><dt>《汤头歌诀》汪昂</dt></p><p><dd>白虎汤用石膏偎，知母甘草粳米陪。亦有加入人参者，躁烦热渴舌生苔。</dd></p><p><dt>《方剂学》邓中甲</dt></p><p><dd>白虎膏知粳米甘，清热生津止渴烦，气分热盛四大证，益气生津人参添。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法下</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="715">第176条</a>  伤寒脉浮滑，此表有热，里有寒，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="4368">白虎汤</a>主之。</dd></p><p><dd>辨阳明病脉证并治法</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="758">第219条</a>  三阳合病，腹满，身重，难以转侧，口<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1678">不仁</a>，面垢，发汗则<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1825">谵语</a>，遗尿。下之则额上生汗，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2122">手足厥冷</a>。若自汗出者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="4368">白虎汤</a>主之。</dd></p><p><dd>辨厥阴病脉证并治法</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="889">第350条</a>  伤寒脉滑而厥者，里有热也，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="4368">白虎汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'白通加猪胆汁汤（伤寒论）','null','<section>
