        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨少阴病脉证并治法</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="853">第314条</a>  少阴病，下利，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="219">白通汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
