    <p>《金匮要略》卷下妇人产后病脉证治第二十一







</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="413">竹叶</a>（一把） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="24748">葛根</a>（三两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="61">防风</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="97">桔梗</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（各一两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>（一枚，炮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（十五枚） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（五两）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="413">竹叶</a>（12g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="24748">葛根</a>（9g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="61">防风</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="97">桔梗</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（各3g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>（6g，炮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（3枚） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（15g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上十味，以水一斗，煮取二升半，分温三服，温复使汗出。颈项强，用大<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>一枚，破之如豆大，前药扬去沫，呕者，加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>半升洗。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>喘热头痛面正红，一防桔桂草参同，葛三姜五附枚一，枣十五枚竹把充。颈项强用大附抵，以大易小不同体，呕为气逆更议加，半夏半升七次洗。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>产后中风，发热，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="acupoint" object-id="191">面正</a>赤，喘而头痛，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="486">竹叶汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'竹叶石膏汤（伤寒论）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《伤寒论》辨阴阳易差后劳复病证并治法第十四









</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="413">竹叶</a>（二把） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="214">石膏</a>（一斤） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>（半升，洗） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="106">麦门冬</a>（一升，去心）<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>（二两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（二两，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="462">粳米</a>（半斤）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="413">竹叶</a>（15g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="214">石膏</a>（48g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>（10g，洗） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="106">麦门冬</a>（20g，去心）<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>（6g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（6g，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="462">粳米</a>（24g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>右七味，以水一斗，煮取六升，去滓，内<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="462">粳米</a>，煮米熟，汤成，去米，温服一升，日三服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>三参二草一斤膏，病后虚羸呕逆叨，粳夏半升叶二把，麦冬还配一升熬。</dd></p><p><dt>《汤头歌诀》汪昂</dt></p><p><dd>竹叶石膏汤人参，麦冬半夏竹叶灵。甘草生姜兼粳米，暑烦热渴脉虚寻。</dd></p><p><dt>《方剂学》邓中甲</dt></p><p><dd>竹叶石膏参麦冬，半夏粳米甘草从，清补气津又和胃，余热耗伤气津用。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨阴阳易差后劳复病证并治法</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="936">第397条</a>  伤寒解后，虚<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1655">羸</a>少气，气逆欲吐者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="237">竹叶石膏汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
