<dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法中</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="607">第68条</a>   发汗，病不解，反恶寒者，虚故也，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="242">芍药甘草附子汤</a>主之。</dd>
