    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="348">茯苓</a>（24g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>（12g，去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（6g，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（3枚，擘）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>右四味，以<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2155">甘澜水</a>一斗，先煮<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="348">茯苓</a>，减二升，内诸药，煮取三升，去滓，温服一升，日三服。</dd></p><p><dd>作<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2155">甘澜水</a>法，取水二斗，置大盆内，以杓扬之，水上有珠子五六千颗相逐，取用之。</dd>
