    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="18">薯蓣</a>（112.5g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="16033">当归</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="635">神曲</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="50">干地黄</a>  <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="603">豆黄卷</a>（各37.5g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（105g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>（26.25g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="21">芎䓖</a>  <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="40">白术</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="106">麦门冬</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="270">杏仁</a>（各22.5g）  <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="95">柴胡</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="97">桔梗</a> <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="348">茯苓</a>（各18.75g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="366">阿胶</a>（26.25g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="123">干姜</a>（11.25g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="48">白敛</a>（7.5g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="61">防风</a>（22.5g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（100枚，为膏）</dd>
    </dl>
