<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd>（方未见）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>体瞤臂肿主藜芦，痫痹风痰俱可驱，芦性升提草甘缓，症详趺蹶遍寻无。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>师曰：病<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1493">趺</a><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1495">蹶</a>，其人但能前，不能却，刺<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1164">腨</a>入二寸，此太阳经伤也。</dd></p><p><dd>病人常以手指臂肿动，此人身体瞤瞤者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="54799">藜芦甘草汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
