','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法下</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="698">第159条</a>  伤寒，服汤药，下利不止，心下<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1348">痞</a>鞭，服<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="407">泻心汤</a>已，复以他药下之，利不止，医以理中与之，利益甚；理中者，理中焦，此利在下焦，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="186">赤石脂禹余粮汤</a>主之，复利不止者，当利其小便。</dd>
