        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>咳而上气，此为肺胀，其人喘，目如脱状，脉浮大者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="313">越婢加半夏汤</a>主之。</dd>
