        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="23211">附子</a>（20g，生用） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="123">干姜</a>（9g，强人可12g）<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（6g，炙）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上三味，以水三升，煮取一升二合，去滓，分温再服。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>一枚生附草姜三，招纳亡阳此指南，外热里寒面赤厥，脉微通脉法中探。</dd></p><p><dd>赤加葱茎用九，腹痛去葱真好手；葱去换芍二两加，呕者生姜二两偶；咽痛去芍桔须加，桔梗一两循经走；脉若不出二两参，桔梗丢开莫掣肘。（加减法）</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>下利<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1846">清谷</a>，里寒外热，汗出而厥者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="222">通脉四逆汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
