    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《长沙方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>一枚附子泻心汤，一两连芩二大黄，汗出恶寒心下痞，专煎轻渍要参详。</dd></p><p><dt>《汤头歌诀》汪昂</dt></p><p><dd>附子泻心用三黄，寒加热药以维阳。痞乃热邪寒药治，恶寒加附治相当。大黄附子汤同意，温药下之妙异常。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨太阳病脉证并治法下</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="695">第156条</a>  心下<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1348">痞</a>，而复恶寒汗出者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="183">附子泻心汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'附子理中汤（重订通俗伤寒论）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
