        <dd>【处方】<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="66">黑附</a>块15g，别直参9g，清<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">炙草</a>2.4g，川姜9g（炒黄），冬<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="40">白术</a>9g（炒香），<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>汁1瓢（冲）。</dd>
