    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>转筋入腹脉微弦，肝气凌脾岂偶然，木畜为鸡其屎土．研来同类妙周旋。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>转筋之为病，其人臂脚直，脉上下行，微弦，转筋入腹者，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="472">鸡屎白散</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'麦门冬汤（金匮要略）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《金匮要略》卷上肺痿肺痈咳嗽上气病脉证治第七







</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="106">麦门冬</a>（七升） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>（一升） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>（二两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（二两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="462">粳米</a>（三合） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（十二枚）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="106">麦门冬</a>（42g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>（6g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>（9g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（6g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="462">粳米</a>（3g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（3枚）</dd>
    </dl>
