        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>辨阳明病脉证并治法</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-extra="%7B%22book_id%22%3A3%7D" object-type="bookchapter" object-id="786">第247条</a>  <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2216">趺阳</a>脉浮而涩，浮则胃气强，涩则小便数，浮涩相搏，大便则难，其脾为约，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="204">麻子仁丸</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
