</p>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>古代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
<dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>（三两，去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（三两，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（十二枚） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a>（六两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（三两） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="634">胶饴</a>（一升）<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="109">黄芪</a>（一两半）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>（9g，去皮） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>（9g，炙） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（3枚） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a>（18g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（9g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="634">胶饴</a>（30g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="109">黄芪</a>（4.5g）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>小建汤加两半芪，诸虚里急治无遗，急当甘缓虚当补，愈信长沙百世师。气短胸满生姜好，三两相加六两讨；如逢腹满胀难消，加茯两半除去枣；及疗肺虚损不足，补气还需开窍早，三两半夏法宜加，蠲除痰饮为至宝。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>虚劳<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1665">里急</a>，诸不足，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="1163">黄芪建中汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>随证化裁</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>气短胸满者，加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>；腹满者，去枣，加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="348">茯苓</a>一两半；及疗肺虚损不足，补气加<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="33">半夏</a>三两。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'黄芪桂枝五物汤（金匮要略）','null','<section>
    <h4>出处</h4>
    <p>《金匮要略》卷上血痹虚劳病脉证并治第六




</p>
