    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>现代剂量</h4>
    <dl>
        <dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="109">黄芪</a>（9g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="42">芍药</a>（9g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="147">桂枝</a>（9g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="118">生姜</a>（18g） <a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="230">大枣</a>（3枚）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
<section>
    <h4>煎服法</h4>
    <dl>
<dd>上五味，以水六升，煮取二升，温服七合，日三服。（一方有<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>）</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
    <section>
        <h4>方歌</h4>
        <dl>
            <dt>《金匮方歌括》陈修园</dt></p><p><dd>血痹如风体不仁，桂枝三两芍芪均，枣枚十二生姜六，须令阳通效自神。</dd>
        </dl>
    </section>
','<section>
    <dl>
<dd>问曰：<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2292">血痹</a>病从何得之？师曰：夫尊荣人<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="25320">骨</a>弱肌肤盛，重因疲劳汗出，卧不时动摇，加被微风遂得之。但以脉自微涩在寸口，关上小紧，宜针引阳气，令脉和、紧去则愈。</dd></p><p><dd><a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="2292">血痹</a>，阴阳俱微，寸口关上微，尺中小紧，外证身体<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="wiki" object-id="1678">不仁</a>，如风痹状，<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="prescription" object-id="299">黄芪桂枝五物汤</a>主之。</dd>
    </dl>
</section>
',null);
INSERT INTO `cmssp_prescription`(`id`, `tag`, `name`, `book`, `summary`, `indications`, `ext_data`) VALUES (null,null,'黄芪芍药桂枝苦酒汤（金匮要略）','null','<section>
