    <dl>
<dd>【处方】<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="133">胆草</a>、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="95">柴胡</a>、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="108">黄芩</a>、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="281">山栀</a>、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="298">连翘</a>、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="76">知母</a>、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="106">麦冬</a>、川连、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="3">人参</a>、<a class="dj-tipinfo" href="javascript:void(0)" object-type="drug" object-id="1">甘草</a>。</dd>
    </dl>
